## Configuration

- Registry: [`scripts/openclaw_company.py`](scripts/openclaw_company.py)
- Per-persona overrides in `.env`: `OPENCLAW_<NAME>_VOICE`, `OPENCLAW_<NAME>_RATE` (e.g. `OPENCLAW_ARGUS_VOICE`, `OPENCLAW_SAGE_RATE`)
- Legacy `FRIDAY_ARGUS_*`, `FRIDAY_EMAIL_NOTIFY_VOICE`, etc. still respected where documented.

## SAGE vs “typing”

**SAGE** speaks only when the Composer JSONL shows a **pre-tool** assistant turn *and* OCR text passes **reasoning** checks — not arbitrary right-pane text, and not after `tool_use` appears. This is intentional to reduce false triggers.

## Agent behaviour

- Refer to the team by name when describing behaviour (“Argus will remind you…”, “Nova announces mail…”).
- Keep tone **professional, warm, occasionally witty** per role — not robotic, not cosplay-heavy.
- Do not rename personae in docs or speech without updating `openclaw_company.py` and `.env`.
